{"id":1278,"date":"2020-05-15T12:46:48","date_gmt":"2020-05-15T12:46:48","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/?p=1278"},"modified":"2021-07-09T08:46:15","modified_gmt":"2021-07-09T08:46:15","slug":"top-cross-platform-app-development-framework-in-2021","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/top-cross-platform-app-development-framework-in-2021","title":{"rendered":"Top Cross-Platform App Development Framework In 2021"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mobile applications have changed businesses to a great extent. Many businesses have created mobile apps for greater reach, and many more are creating them.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Technology is always unstable, so you cannot always stick to old technologies, if you have to move forward, you have to use new technologies. According to the stats, in 2019, 118 billion mobile apps have downloaded globally, and it is going to increase in the upcoming years. With this continuous growth in mobile application usage, we can guess that app downloads will increase by up to 400 billion by 2022.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So it\u2019s important to choose the right platform for your app. The <a href=\"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/native-vs-hybrid-app-choose-the-best-aryausa\">Native App Development gives you more control<\/a>, but it struggles with native IDEs and SDKs.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Working in a cross-platform app is much easier.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cross-platform frameworks have made mobile app development cost-effective. Businesses choose cross-platform app development over native because of lesser development time and cost.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Using Cross-Platform Frameworks, you can launch applications with a single codebase.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400; color: #000000;\">What is the Cross-Platform Framework?<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The cross-platform framework is the framework used to develop a mobile application that can run on any device and operating system like Android and iOS. It empowers the components to write the code once and use it for any platform. These apps are cost-effective and enable access to a broad range of software\/hardware.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400; color: #000000;\">Why does the market move towards Hybrid Apps?<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are many benefits to choosing a cross-platform for your business mobile app like cost-effective development, uniform look across all devices, code reusability, faster development.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><a href=\"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Cross-Platform-App-Development-Company-2021.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-2370\" src=\"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Cross-Platform-App-Development-Company-2021.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"435\" height=\"435\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Cross-Platform-App-Development-Company-2021.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Cross-Platform-App-Development-Company-2021-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Cross-Platform-App-Development-Company-2021-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Cross-Platform-App-Development-Company-2021-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 435px) 100vw, 435px\" \/><\/a><\/h2>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400; color: #000000;\">Benefits of cross-platform apps<\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cost-Effective<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The single code base for various platforms<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Easy cloud integration<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Wider Reach\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fewer Barriers in terms of Native applications<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400; color: #000000;\">Best Cross-platforms Frameworks<\/span><\/h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><b> Flutter<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Flutter is a free and open-source UI Framework used for developing apps for web and mobile and desktop with a single codebase. It is launched by Google. It provides a great native experience for both Android and iOS apps with its widgets<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><strong>Pros<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Responsive\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fast development<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Great UI<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Cons<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Limited libraries<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><b> React Native<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">React Native is the most popular cross-platform mobile app development framework. It supports Javascript codebase. It is used for developing innovative mobile apps for Android and iOS platforms. React Native framework has a large number of built-in components. It enables developers to build apps in cross-platform with minimal effort that provides a native experience to end-users.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><strong>Pros<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">JavaScript-based\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Good Performance<\/span><b>\u00a0<\/b><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Cons<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Compatibility issue<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><b> Ionic<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ionic is an open-source framework for developing mobile apps and progressive web apps. It is used basically for front-end development.\u00a0 Designed on top of Angular, Ionic offers tools and services for building hybrid apps using technologies like HTML and SaaS.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><strong>Pros<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Easy to use and learn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fast prototyping<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Cons\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Performance and security<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><b> Xamarin<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Xamarin is also a free, open-source cross-platform app framework that is used to develop applications for Android, iOS, and Windows. It allows you to share 75% of code across different platforms to make your development faster.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><strong>\u00a0Pros<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Performance<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Easy to maintain<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Cons\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Higher Cost<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><b> Phone Gap<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">PhoneGap is the best cross-platform app development framework based on JavaScript. It provides high performance and Debugging is very easy with popular web inspectors tools in each browser. Knowledge of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript is sufficient to get started with PhoneGap app development.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pros<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fast Testing<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fast Deployment<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cons\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">UI<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Final Thoughts:<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whenever you are trying to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/is-flutter-the-future-of-mobile-app-development\">hire a Cross-Platform App Developer<\/a> for your business,\u00a0 selecting the right mobile app framework is very important. If you are still confused about which framework to choose for your project, then reach out to us, We&#8217;re one of the top leading Mobile App Development companies in USA. we&#8217;re delivering the mobile apps according to your needs.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><script type=\"application\/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https:\/\/schema.org\",\n  \"@type\": \"BlogPosting\",\n  \"mainEntityOfPage\": {\n    \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n    \"@id\": \"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/top-cross-platform-app-development-framework-in-2021\"\n  },\n  \"headline\": \"Top Cross-Platform App Development Framework In 2021\",\n  \"description\": \"Mobile applications have changed businesses to a great extent. Many businesses have created mobile apps for greater reach, and many more are creating it.\",\n  \"image\": [\n    \"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Top-Cross-platform-ap